<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvari hehpih hung lang khah,
 Khangthak in gen zel unau;
 Kumsawt inle tin zo puona,
 Chawihatna mai (3) ading in.

[V2]
 2. Van lahaw laka khun ziehi,'
 Lulpen hilo thei puona;
 Kingkang thiengtho bawl ding pen chuh,
 Thillul pahchak (3) ahi zing.

[V3]
 3. Belam No thisan hi theih mak!
 Thagau tatdawk a nat zie;
 Seraf Aw nem phak sang inle,
 Ana sang zing (3) sek ahi.

[V4]
 4. Khangthak tamtak beih nung inle,
 Pa'k le kipan bang ahi;
 Etnawp mak tak thillul hidi'n,
 Lang zel ina (3) a thuk ngal.

[V5]
 5. Kumsawt in a kipiek lulzie,
 Hilhchet zawh guol ahi puoi;
 Ngaih phakloh hun nungin ziehi,
 A thak zing hi (3) bangtik inle.

[V6]
 6. Aw hawih simsen loh nei ta leng,
 Pahchak hun ka gingcha puoi;
 Ka Aw neihsun hawih mahmah leh,
 Ka ti na e (3) chawihat na'n.</lyrics>
<title>DEEMSTER</title>
<hymn_number>68</hymn_number>
</song>